  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/414fa9955f857886e17931dfc76fd6af.poster.avif?t=1770404391\" width=590 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/414fa9955f857886e17931dfc76fd6af.webm?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/414fa9955f857886e17931dfc76fd6af.mp4?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command an ancient starship and fight your way to the heart of a dying Empire. Fend off attacks from demented cultists, craven space pirates, and xenophobic Imperial soldiers. Discover powerful artifacts and use them to build your ship into a fearsome war engine. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage Your Ship</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your starship is a mighty and terrible vessel, brimming with arcane technology and devastating weapons. Harness your ship's weapons, modules, and reactor power to maximize your combat potential.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Powerful Combos</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrange your upgrades into powerful combos and use them to surgically dismantle your enemies. But watch out. They can do exactly the same to you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Your Crew</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enlist crew from six different factions. Customize them with a vast array of wargear and engage in bloody, strategic boarding actions against enemy craft. Watch them crush their foes or die horrifically in the frenzy of void warfare. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Everchanging Galaxy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience hundreds of randomly generated encounters. Navigate through a brutal and unrelenting galaxy, weaving together a new story with every run.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dark Techno-Gothic Future</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet technocultist magi, Imperial deserters, demon lords and more. Recruit them, fight them, and make choices that impact the state of your ship and the lives of your crew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/cb1dfb25564286ccb0f06ea20dbebefe.poster.avif?t=1770404391\" width=590 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/cb1dfb25564286ccb0f06ea20dbebefe.webm?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/cb1dfb25564286ccb0f06ea20dbebefe.mp4?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/1bacc6917b52728ce440d566a2802425.poster.avif?t=1770404391\" width=590 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/1bacc6917b52728ce440d566a2802425.webm?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/1bacc6917b52728ce440d566a2802425.mp4?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/ed00f83c76999f647db9ad7037eb8681.poster.avif?t=1770404391\" width=590 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/ed00f83c76999f647db9ad7037eb8681.webm?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/ed00f83c76999f647db9ad7037eb8681.mp4?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/69790d0de4a06dfc2fc27f27f972e612.poster.avif?t=1770404391\" width=590 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/69790d0de4a06dfc2fc27f27f972e612.webm?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/69790d0de4a06dfc2fc27f27f972e612.mp4?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/414fa9955f857886e17931dfc76fd6af.poster.avif?t=1770404391\" width=590 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/414fa9955f857886e17931dfc76fd6af.webm?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/414fa9955f857886e17931dfc76fd6af.mp4?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command an ancient starship and fight your way to the heart of a dying Empire. Fend off attacks from demented cultists, craven space pirates, and xenophobic Imperial soldiers. Discover powerful artifacts and use them to build your ship into a fearsome war engine. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage Your Ship</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your starship is a mighty and terrible vessel, brimming with arcane technology and devastating weapons. Harness your ship's weapons, modules, and reactor power to maximize your combat potential.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Powerful Combos</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrange your upgrades into powerful combos and use them to surgically dismantle your enemies. But watch out. They can do exactly the same to you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Your Crew</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enlist crew from six different factions. Customize them with a vast array of wargear and engage in bloody, strategic boarding actions against enemy craft. Watch them crush their foes or die horrifically in the frenzy of void warfare. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Everchanging Galaxy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience hundreds of randomly generated encounters. Navigate through a brutal and unrelenting galaxy, weaving together a new story with every run.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dark Techno-Gothic Future</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet technocultist magi, Imperial deserters, demon lords and more. Recruit them, fight them, and make choices that impact the state of your ship and the lives of your crew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/cb1dfb25564286ccb0f06ea20dbebefe.poster.avif?t=1770404391\" width=590 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/cb1dfb25564286ccb0f06ea20dbebefe.webm?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/cb1dfb25564286ccb0f06ea20dbebefe.mp4?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/1bacc6917b52728ce440d566a2802425.poster.avif?t=1770404391\" width=590 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/1bacc6917b52728ce440d566a2802425.webm?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/1bacc6917b52728ce440d566a2802425.mp4?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/ed00f83c76999f647db9ad7037eb8681.poster.avif?t=1770404391\" width=590 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853590/extras/ed00f83c76999f647db9ad7037eb8681.webm?t=1770404391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shar